research_municipality_step.notes: Information was gathered from the official City of Somerville, TX website and the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory. The official city website lists Laura Hoover as Mayor Pro-tem, while the Texas Municipal League directory lists Delfino Orozco as Mayor Pro Tem and Laura Hoover as an Alderperson. The official city website's designation for Mayor Pro-tem was prioritized. 'Alderman' and 'Alderperson' roles were standardized to 'Council Member'.
